code: import axios from'axios';var baseUrl='/api/notes';var getAll=function getAll(){var q=axios.get(baseUrl);return q.then(function(s){return s.data;});};var create=function create(newObject){var q=axios.post(baseUrl,newObject);return q.then(function(s){return s.data;});};var update=function update(id,newObject){var q=axios.put("".concat(baseUrl,"/").concat(id),newObject);return q.then(function(s){return s.data;});};export default{getAll:getAll,create:create,update:update};
